\ examples/19-conway-blinker.6th — Conway's Game of Life on substrate grid.
\
\ Same STEP-CA primitive that ran Rule 90 / Rule 110 / Rule 184 runs Conway
\ on a 5×5 Moore-grid.  Verifies the vertical blinker oscillation
\ (period 2) — Conway-rule applied to substrate features via NSUM.

use prelude
use peano
use graph
use debug

: conway
  dup NSUM "cw-sum" store
  NGET "cw-st" store
  "cw-sum" load 3 = if 1 else
    "cw-sum" load 2 = "cw-st" load 1 = * if 1 else 0 then
  then ;

\ 5×5 grid: 25 cells, row-major ids 1..25.
MARK MARK MARK MARK MARK
MARK MARK MARK MARK MARK
MARK MARK MARK MARK MARK
MARK MARK MARK MARK MARK
MARK MARK MARK MARK MARK
drop drop drop drop drop drop drop drop drop drop
drop drop drop drop drop drop drop drop drop drop
drop drop drop drop drop

NODES 25 assert-eq

